      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KARINYA TOM TOM (1) continues to build a strong record and was impressive winner in quick time last start when scoring by 2 lengths (19.71) at Gunnedah. Has an impeccable record here. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Ideally placed to take this out. HEIDI KEEPING (2) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from four starts. Was out of the placings last time (23.43) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 12 lengths. Among the main chances. KIANDO HUNT (8) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at Temora over 330m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from six starts. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. BOGAN KNOWS (3) can fill a top-three spot.",
